Hey, {tag:0}! This your first time here?
{pageend:Welcome to Sinnoh’s Grand Underground!}
This is a network of tunnels, caves, and caverns
{pageend:lying beneath Sinnoh.}
Huh? What am I doing down in this expanse of
{pageend:a place?}
That’s kind of hard to answer. I mean, you can do
{pageend:pretty much anything you want down here.}
For instance, you can dig up Fossils and treasure,
{pageend:or you can make your own Secret Base.}
You should talk to the Underground Man in
{pageend:Eterna City to learn more.}
Y is the way to go back to the surface!
{pageend:Remember: Y!}
I have to get going now. I’ll see you around!

{pageend:Thank you!}
